    "yg_info_CT6wLn": {
      "type": "yg-info",
      "settings": {
        "title": "Find the best folding electric bike",
        "richtext": "<p>Folding electric bikes are easy to store and transport. They can be quickly folded into a compact size, making them easy to fit in the trunk of a car, carry on public transportation, or store in a small space. actbest <strong>folding electric bikes</strong> offer a variety of models. You can choose based on your commuting habits, the terrain you ride on, and the storage conditions; for long commutes, choose a model with a long range.</p><h3>Compact Folding Electric Bikes</h3><p>Compact folding electric bikes are the ultimate companions for city dwellers. Their design prioritizes convenience and maneuverability. It's a breeze to navigate crowded city streets with these bikes. After the ride is over, folding them is a quick and easy process. In just a few seconds, you can turn them into a compact form that's easy to carry. This makes them suitable for public transportation such as buses or subways. If you live in a small apartment or work with limited storage space, you can hide them in a corner, under a desk, or even in a closet.</p><h3>Folding Three-Wheel Electric Bikes</h3><p><a href=\"https://actbestbike.com/products/triker-folding-3-wheels-electric-bike\" title=\"Folding 3 Wheels Electric Bike\">Folding three-wheel electric bikes</a> are an excellent choice for those looking for enhanced stability. These electric tricycles have excellent stability and are suitable for all types of riders. Elderly people, beginners and people with poor physical coordination can easily learn to ride. Their open or closed rear compartments provide ample storage space. Small vendors can use them to transport goods for sale, while families can carry large items such as furniture. It is a practical and versatile choice for a variety of needs.</p><h3>Why choose Actbestbike folding electric bike?</h3><p><strong>Actbestbike folding electric bikes</strong> have excellent long-distance capabilities and strong performance. Our folding electric bikes are equipped with high-capacity batteries, with a range of at least 30 miles on a single charge, and some models can even reach 65 miles. Whether it is daily commuting or long-distance travel on weekends, there is no need to worry about power issues. In terms of performance, the motor power ranges from 500W to 1000W. The 1000W motor can help fast acceleration and easy climbing, and can ride smoothly even on steep slopes; on flat roads, the 500W motor can meet the speed and power requirements, providing reliable protection for riding on different terrains.</p><p>Explore more high-quality electric bikes on actbest: <a href=\"https://actbestbike.com/collections/fat-tire-electric-bike\" title=\"fat tire ebike\">fat tire ebike</a> | <a href=\"https://actbestbike.com/collections/commuter-ebike\" title=\"Commuter electric bikes\">commuter electric bikes</a> | <a href=\"https://actbestbike.com/collections/best-sellers\" title=\"Best Selling Electric Bikes\">best selling electric eikes</a></p>",
